      <item>Task 026 (D2-16) — `InsightsResponseRenderer` two-path React component
        (playbook structured envelope + RAG citation-grounded prose). Consumes this
        tool's responses. P2-G6.</item>
      <item>Task 027 (D2-17) — Clickable citations (v1.1 `citations[].href`; v1.0
        display-name-only fallback). Builds on task 026. P2-G6.</item>
      <item>Task 028 (D2-18) — Confidence floor badge (`&lt;0.6` → "low-confidence"
        hint per integration brief §6 question 5 + R5 decision D5). Builds on task
        026. P2-G6.</item>
      <item>Task 019 (D2-09) — Slash command `/ask-insights` semantic extension. Sets
        `forceMode` for unambiguous invocation per spec FR-12 / SC-17. The slash
        command path calls this tool with `forceMode` set; natural-language LLM
        tool-call path leaves it absent.</item>
      <item>Task 015 (D2-05) — `InvokeSummarizePlaybookTool`. Sibling tool;
        description must differentiate per NFR-12. The UR-01 risk centers on these
        two tools' routing disambiguation.</item>
