        cross-reference to task 015's description).
      - Chosen gating capability (existing constant reused vs new
        `PlaybookCapabilities.InsightsQuery` added).
      - Config key for `Bff:BaseAddress` (or repo convention used).
      - Routing smoke-test traces (positive + negative prompts).
      - Correlation-id propagation evidence (App Insights / Kusto trace IDs).
      - `forceMode` test results (slash command vs natural-language).
      - 12 error code mapping results.
      - Zone B boundary grep result.
      - BFF publish-size delta.
      - CVE scan result.
      Report task completion.
    </step>
  </steps>

